summary: WARNING: This is unfinished and needs finishing. If you want a template to make your own home use this.
descriptionHtml:
I built this player home with only vanilla assets. I took me a while to make and I hope you guys can use it as a template for your own player home.

This was a player home I was working on before Fallout 4 was announced. When Fallout 4 got announced I got distracted because I wanted to prepare for the next gen Creation Kit.

Everyone is allowed to use this in their player home creations. I would love to see this player home finished but I didn't have the time to finish it. Sorry if it looks bad that I put unfinished work on the Nexus. I really wanted people to have this player home mod and I didn't prepare for Fallout 4 to be announced so quickly xD

So feel free to use this in your creations. I give all permission for use in other projects.

If you manage to finish it, I would love to see it!
author: StormEagle150
